OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMelvin Van Peebles:        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'Godfather of black cinema'
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdies at 89                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Pioneering filmmaker Melvin Van        
OL,6, Peebles, dubbed the "godfather of black
OL,7, cinema", has died aged 89, with        
OL,8, directors Spike Lee, Ava DuVernay and  
OL,9, Barry Jenkins leading the tributes.    
OL,11,FVan Peebles, famous for 1970s films    
OL,12,Fincluding Watermelon Man and Sweet     
OL,13,FSweetback's Baadasssss Song, died at   
OL,14,Fhome in New York on Tuesday.           
OL,16,FA family statement paid tribute to his 
OL,17,F"relentless innovation".               
OL,19,FOscar-winner Lee said: "Damn, we have  
OL,20,Flost another giant!"                   
